s-serif;font-size:11px;line-height:15px;color:#666666;\">&dagger;Current and previous Nordstrom credit cardmembers and Nordstrom employees are not eligible for this offer. The $40 Nordstrom Note can be used once it has been delivered to your loyalty account. To be eligible for the offer, you must apply and get approved for a new Nordstrom credit card. This Nordstrom Note may be delivered to your loyalty account in 7&ndash;10 business days from the credit card application approval date. The Nordstrom Note will be awarded only to the Nordstrom cardmember and cannot be applied as a statement credit or payment. Offer terms subject to change or cancellation at any time. For complete Nordy Club program details, go to <a href=\"https://www.nordstrom.com/browse/nordy-club/terms-conditions\" style=\"color:#666666;text-decoration:underline;\">nordstrom.com/nordyterms</a>.</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 12px 0;font-family:sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:16px;color:#000000;\">This is an advertising message from Nordstrom.</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 12px 0;font-family:sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:16px;color:#000000;\">For complete Nordy Club program details, go to <a href=\"https://www.nordstrom.com/browse/nordy-club/terms-conditions\" style=\"color:#000001;text-decoration:underline;\">nordstrom.com/nordyterms</a>.</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 12px 0;font-family:sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:16px;color:#000000;\">FREE SHIPPING. FREE RETURNS. This offer is only available for standard shipping on Nordstrom.com. Please visit Nordstromrack.com for details about their shipping and return policies.</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 12px 0;font-family:sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:16px;color:#000000;\">Add <a href=\"mailto:nordstrom@eml.nordstrom.com\" style=\"color:#000001;text-decoration:underline;\">nordstrom@eml.nordstrom.com</a> to your address book to ensure that you receive our emails in your inbox.</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 12px 0;font-family:sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:16px;color:#000000;\">NORDSTROM, 1600 Seventh Avenue, Suite 2600, Seattle, WA 98101</p><p style=\"margin:0;font-family:sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:16px;color:#000000;\"><a href=\"https://www.nordstrom.com/browse/customer-service/policy/privacy\" style=\"color:#000001;text-decoration:underline;\">Nordstrom Privacy Policy</a><br>&copy;2026 Nordstrom</p></div></div></div>",
